  "You will not be." He slowed as they neared her quarters. They apperared 
before her door. He turned to her....did a little bow kissed her hand and 
said his goodnights and proceeded to his quarters to get some sleep. Unlike 
most bots destructor was forced to sleep in a cr chamber. His powers needed 
to be rejuvenated once every month there. He arrived at his quarters locked 
the door and went to sleep.
